This map will try to explain the basics of
how to play the game in an interactive manner.

You win the game by capturing all regions that
are controled by opposing forces.

Before we can start crushing our enemies,
we need to learn how to control the game.
To move the camera. You can do this by
hovering the mouse by the edge of the window.

