text = "Good job!

When you run out of first actions, you enter the second
phase of your turn \"mobilization\".

Here you can click on your cities with excess power to turn that
power into bonus actions. If a city has only 1 power, you cannot
turn that power into bonus actions.

Once you are done mobilizing, click the button in the bottom right
corner to advance to the last phase."
horizontal_alignment = 1
